title: Andrew Schulz on Culture Vulture Accusations, Gangs, Gringo Papi & More
description:
#AndrewSchulz pulled to chop it up with Adam, AD, and Doknow for a fire episode! He talks about his beef with Joe Budden, his friendship with Charlamagne, Joe Rogan, being independent, performing two nights at Radio City, his special #Infamous, and more!

-----
00:00 Intro
6:31 Andrew says Adam just met Black people and he can tell
8:06 The case of Tyga and Ay Caramba, Doknow vs OG Cholo
9:58 Andrew thought Doknow was an industry plant
12:02 Adam spits a few hilarious bars
17:02 Andrew be tuned in to No Jumper universe, mentioned T-Rell and Sharp many times, loves the NJ clips channel
26:43 Sometimes your opps could be a family member
28:14 Doknow got s___ while being on house arrest once, he knew the dude, grew up with him
36:35 Joe Budden said Andrew is using his hip hop fanbase
48:29 Adam is left out of cookouts and he wants to go so bad, he used to throw pies at security guards
49:50 Andrew asks if AD and Doknow have ever "seen" a drive-by
50:35 It's ok for YG to show appreciation for the culture because he pays homage and respects the culture as opposed to Tyga
58:00 Doknow is trying to find the balance between making jokes about everything and giving his opinion: "Not everything's funny"
1:10:18 Andrew is one of the few white guys who can make jokes about other cultures
1:11:55 A____ talk, when you should start paying child support?
1:14:30 Andrew explains his a_____ clinic joke
1:17:14 Brendan Schaub's Gringo Papi special backlash
1:28:12 Andrew did Radio City twice, that's 12000 people
1:39:13 Adam let AD do what to his mom?
1:42:35 Andrew wanna know if Adam was _____ as a kid
1:45:25 How Clinton pardoned Adam's dad and the whole Monica situation
1:47:52 Andrew speaks on how Monica was hated and the villain in the whole Clinton situation, it wouldn't happen like that nowadays
2:00:51 Joe Rogan is the man, he possibly spent 50k just to do Andrew's podcast
2:10:51 Andrew explains that Jada and Chris Rock been having beef all the way leading up to the Will slap
